    "body": "Reproduced it easily by sending a message with image and then put focus on image and clicked on the Up arrow\nWorking on a fix. \n\nEdit : \nI just got the understanding of the edit message feature triggered with the Key_Up press. \n\nSo this feature enables the user to edit the last message. Based on the code base, this feature is triggered when the `StatusChatInput` receives events.\n\nWhat we are trying to achieve is bring consistency between this Edit on Key_Up press in StatusChatInput and the Key_Right click from a mouse in order to trigger the Edit or the contextual menu that contains the Edit message.\n\n",
